column2: Dagoth Ur is at the undisputed apex of power.
Dagoth Ur's power is very strong.
Dagoth Ur is pursuing a policy of aggressive militarism, using dreams of war to guide worshippers.
Dagoth Ur is using dreams to invite new worshippers.
Dagoth Ur is focusing on internal affairs, mostly ignoring outsiders.
Isolated within the inner sanctum and only willing to speak with closest servants, Dagoth Ur is focused on greater matters.
Dagoth Ur is in state of deep meditation, and as such, completely unreachable.
